    "kind": "chord"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 166.6,
    "text": "望⽇落在極處出現　沉下去一息間天已黑",
    "kind": "lyric-or-other"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 181.9,
    "text": "         Fm                 C/E              Dm         G13",
    "kind": "chord"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 197.9,
    "text": "平靜世界那個你快將⼊眠　睡一遍　明天⾒",
    "kind": "lyric-or-other"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 213.3,
    "text": "C                                Gm                     F",
    "kind": "chord"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 229.3,
    "text": "烈⽇慢慢盛放海⾯　還為你暖透了冬天那花蕊",
    "kind": "lyric-or-other"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 244.6,
    "text": "         Fm                 C/E              Dm         G13",
    "kind": "chord"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 260.6,
    "text": "如若太記掛我等不到⽩天　花瓣藏一片",
    "kind": "lyric-or-other"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 276.0,
    "text": "       Am           E/G#       Gm             F              Fm",
    "kind": "chord"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 292.0,
    "text": "延續了四季像⾸舊調　愛煞你看我會不經意的笑",
    "kind": "lyric-or-other"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 307.3,
    "text": "   C/E             Bb                G7sus",
    "kind": "chord"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 323.4,
    "text": "地球哪天不破曉　以你笑臉普照",
    "kind": "lyric-or-other"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 354.4,
    "text": "            C            Em             F                C   G/B",
    "kind": "chord"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 370.4,
    "text": "抱起了幾千攝⽒陽光　來讓相戀近乎熱燙",
    "kind": "lyric-or-other"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 385.7,
    "text": "        Am                 D/F#               F                 G",
    "kind": "chord"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 401.8,
    "text": "如淚要落下　待我瞬間⾛訪　能在光速間　蒸發絕望",
    "kind": "lyric-or-other"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 417.1,
    "text": "          C               Em           F           C   G/B",
    "kind": "chord"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 433.1,
    "text": "抱起了幾千攝⽒陽光　這溫暖不趕不慌",
    "kind": "lyric-or-other"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 448.4,
    "text": "    Am                 D/F#     F          G                C",
    "kind": "chord"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 464.5,
    "text": "世界沒有光　⽕花如驟降　靠我掌⼼給你釋放",
    "kind": "lyric-or-other"
  },
  {
    "page": 1,
    "top": 495.5,
